# English only (strict)

All project text must be in English: documentation, code comments, commit messages, PR descriptions, and user-facing strings added by agents.

# Code comments

Add detailed English comments for non-obvious logic:

- Yggdrasil/Mojang protocol compatibility
- UUID/id derivation and hashing
- hybrid storage and lazy migration
- session validation and texture signing
- intentional spec deviations

Do not comment trivial or self-explanatory code.
